>
<ParallaxHeader client:idle />
<div style="margin: 50px">
<section>
  <h1>🔧 Cooktop Repair by Zaricci</h1>
  <p><strong>White-Glove Service for Luxury Gas, Induction &amp; Electric Cooktops</strong></p>
  <p>A luxury cooktop is the engine of a gourmet kitchen — sleek, responsive, and designed for precision. When it fails, even slightly, it disrupts the flow of your day. At Zaricci, we offer expert cooktop repair services for luxury homes, chefs, and design-conscious homeowners who expect nothing less than performance perfection.</p>
  <p>Whether it's a smart induction cooktop or a custom gas range top, we treat every repair with care, discretion, and industry-leading expertise.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>🛠️ Specializing in Elite Cooktop Brands</h2>
  <p>Our technicians are certified in the repair and calibration of the world’s finest cooktop brands, including:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Wolf</li>
    <li>Thermador</li>
    <li>Miele</li>
    <li>Gaggenau</li>
    <li>JennAir</li>
    <li>Monogram</li>
    <li>Bosch Benchmark</li>
    <li>La Cornue</li>
    <li>Viking</li>
    <li>Bertazzoni</li>
    <li>Café by GE</li>
    <li>Electrolux ICON</li>
    <li>Fisher &amp; Paykel</li>
    <li>Smeg</li>
    <li>Samsung Chef Collection</li>
    <li>KitchenAid Architect Series</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We’re equipped to repair induction, gas, electric, glass-ceramic, and hybrid cooktops with full respect for your cabinetry, surfaces, and home environment.</p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>🔍 Common Luxury Cooktop Issues We Fix</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Burners won’t ignite or heat evenly</li>
    <li>Induction cooktop not detecting cookware</li>
    <li>Cracked glass or ceramic surface</li>
    <li>Inconsistent temperature control</li>
    <li>Touch controls unresponsive</li>
    <li>Gas smell or clicking without ignition</li>
    <li>Error codes or smart sensor issues</li>
    <li>Downdraft vent not operating properly</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>🌟 Why Homeowners Trust Zaricci</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Same-Day Cooktop Repair in high-end Los Angeles neighborhoods</li>
    <li>Certified Luxury Appliance Technicians</li>
    <li>No Subcontractors — Only In-House Experts</li>
    <li>Discreet, No-Trace Repairs using protective coverings and care</li>
    <li>OEM Parts Only for longevity and brand integrity</li>
    <li>Post-Repair Testing to ensure every feature functions flawlessly</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>🌍 We Proudly Serve</h2>
  <p>Zaricci provides luxury cooktop repair to homes and estates in:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Los Angeles</li>
    <li>Beverly Hills</li>
    <li>Brentwood</li>
    <li>Malibu</li>
    <li>Calabasas</li>
    <li>Pasadena</li>
    <li>Santa Monica</li>
    <li>Newport Beach</li>
    <li>Irvine</li>
    <li>Ventura County</li>
    <li>and more</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>🧰 Preventative Maintenance for Premium Cooktops</h2>
  <p>Luxury cooktops perform best with seasonal maintenance. We offer custom tune-up services to clean, inspect, and recalibrate burners, sensors, vents, and glass surfaces — all aligned with your brand’s standards and warranty recommendations.</p>
</section>

</div>
<h2>Areas We Serve For Cooktop Repair</h2>
<Areas client:visible/>
</Layout>